    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございました。みなさんがいたから\nここまで歌えたんだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. I don’t think I could have\nsung this far without you all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7,
      "endTime": 12.300000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "最高の決勝戦にしてね\n長瀬麻奈……いえ、お姉さんが夢見たステージに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Make it the best finals ever.\nOn the stage that Mana Nagase… no‚ your sister dreamed of.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5,
      "endTime": 22.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "私も、瑠依と同じように、もっと成長する\nあなたの姉を超えるためにも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to grow even more‚ just like Rui.\nSo I can surpass your sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5,
      "endTime": 28.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.133333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "はい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.133333333333333,
      "endTime": 30.099999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "次に戦う時は、負けない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t lose the next time we fight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3,
      "endTime": 33.07095227241516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "……終わったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It’s over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.36666666666667,
      "endTime": 36.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……うん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.166666666666664,
      "endTime": 38.099999999999994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、負けちゃったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ we lost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3,
      "endTime": 40.94999990463256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "悔しくないと言えばウソになるけど……\n悔いはないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’d be a lie to say I’m not frustrated…\nbut I have no regrets.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.44999990463256,
      "endTime": 46.116666571299234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.28333323796589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "……莉央、さっき\nどうして琴乃にあんなこと言ったのさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rio‚ why\ndid you say that to Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.28333323796589,
      "endTime": 50.283333285649604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.7833332379659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "僕達は解散するんだ\nLizNoirに次はないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re disbanding.\nThere won’t be a next time for LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7833332379659,
      "endTime": 55.172925217946364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.649999904632566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "くすっ、私意地っ張りなのよ\n貴方なら知ってるでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kus‚ I’m stubborn‚ you know.\nYou know that‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.649999904632566,
      "endTime": 60.74999990463257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.94999990463256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "…………\nうん、そうだね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "………\nYeah‚ that’s true…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.94999990463256,
      "endTime": 65.98333323796591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.18333323796588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "僕のパートナーは、意地っ張りで頑固で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My partner was a stubborn and headstrong…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.18333323796588,
      "endTime": 70.4745804150899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.9745804150899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "どんな逆境にぶつかっても\n絶対に諦めない強い女の子だった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…strong girl who never gave up‚\nno matter what adversity she faced…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9745804150899,
      "endTime": 77.52895682652789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.01872704823809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "そんな、莉央を\n僕は、勝たせてあげたかった……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to…\nmake her win…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.01872704823809,
      "endTime": 82.61872723897295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.1187270482381
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "僕は、怪我をして\n莉央の足を引っ張って……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I got injured‚\nand held Rio back…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1187270482381,
      "endTime": 88.0187270482381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.21872704823812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央、ごめん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ I’m sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.21872704823812,
      "endTime": 91.33548448880514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.83548448880514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、葵……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Aoi…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.83548448880514,
      "endTime": 94.10215137799584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.26881782213842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "私のために、泣いてくれなくても……\nもう、いいのよ、葵",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t have to cry for me…\nIt’s okay now‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.26881782213842,
      "endTime": 99.47491761843358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.96708313624062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_04_05-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん、莉央、ごめん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ Rio. I’m sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.96708313624062,
      "endTime": 105.19792219797768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.69792219797768
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
